<div class="jumbotron col-md-12 jumbotron-bkgrdImg">
    <h1>Northwest Labs</h1>
    <br />
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <p class="lead">Northwest Labs is one of the leading organizations in pharmaceutical research and testing. Many large organizations use our advanced chemical compound testing methods to get their products approved and into market!</p>
        <!--Link to a review of "northwest labs" (not. Could be reviews drawn from a database or a simple link to a yelp page-->
